{"tid":610422,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[自作孽] 短途旅行都去唔成","createTime":"2018-03-30T02:26:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T13:57:36.000Z","uid":5241,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"eb2db30a269551e9335d1a6d24f27f058216849a","tid":610422,"uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T02:26:53.000Z","msg":"是咁的，本身打算復活節連假去個小旅行經廈門去金門，一早買左飛，我認我on99唔知香港啲旅行團原來會集體搭深圳地鐵去高鐵站，過關過安檢都等左好耐，最後高鐵開果時我仲喺福田口岸站，想碰下運氣去睇下有冇下班車結果都full哂了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n傷心欲絕到想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去返福田食早餐，食完就返香港了。<br />\n<br />\n羨慕去到旅行嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b01a9012132aae8059da01a707e0eb9a515b6c2","tid":610422,"uid":5241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T02:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/30/103613_8408bd44f5471af3e58e76029bd58487.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F103613_8408bd44f5471af3e58e76029bd58487.png&h=302b87ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/30/103647_d13413959f8cf2e0367d5129d337f5e9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F103647_d13413959f8cf2e0367d5129d337f5e9.png&h=9607aef8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係好唔開心呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a535e99eac930b16730038a51b8f49d1243edc01","tid":610422,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T02:46:08.000Z","msg":"姐係點？<br />\n跟旅行團但係遲到？"},{"pid"