By":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T07:58:23.000Z","msg":"即係點?<br />\n你想walkin買飛但比其他旅行團塞爆晒?<br />\n所以冇飛買坐唔到高鐵所以要返轉頭?"},{"pid":"df7b0e3df15252c6d6c8d888ad26f90517c2978b","tid":610422,"uid":157247,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T08:29:04.000Z","msg":"係咪你已經買左高鐵飛，但因為太多人上唔到地鐵，去到高鐵站個時班車已經走左又買唔到下一班既飛？<br />\n<br />\n睇左幾次都以為你join左旅行團但去錯集合地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649919697c8527b9b558a5b20f9c5da96b87365a","tid":610422,"uid":71543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T08:53:47.000Z","msg":"絲打你啲旅記死晒圖<br />\n有冇可能睇返有圖版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35206cf9a4c0c1989999de2baf419740400563ae","tid":610422,"uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df7b0e3df15252c6d6c8d888ad26f90517c2978b","tid":610422,"uid":157247,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T08:29:04.000Z","msg":"係咪你已經買左高鐵飛，但因為太多人上唔到地鐵，去到高鐵站個時班車已經走左又買唔到下一班既飛？<br />\n<br />\n睇左幾次都以為你join左旅行團但去錯集合地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T09:27:37.000Z","msg":"係，對唔住，我岩岩個人太顧亂打野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你幫我整合"},{"pid":"a82fd867a66ffd24d6736562046605ef5dce1611","tid":610422,"uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"649919697c8527b9b558a5b20f9c5da96b87365a","tid":610422,"uid":71543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T08:53:47.000Z","msg":"絲打你啲旅記死晒圖<br />\n有冇可能睇返有圖版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T09:28:00.000Z","msg":"有死哂咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  高登果d？"},{"pid":"0dac54b51866969ae2ccab49e622d1e1760669ed","tid":610422,"uid":71543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a82fd867a66ffd24d6736562046605ef5dce1611","tid":610422,"uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"649919697c8527b9b558a5b20f9c5da96b87365a","tid":610422,"uid":71543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T08:53:47.000Z","msg":"絲打你啲旅記死晒圖<br />\n有冇可能睇返有圖版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T09:28:00.000Z","msg":"有死哂咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  高登果d？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T09:29:31.000Z","msg":"高登同連登舊個啲都死左圖<br />\n之前連登個個up圖網死左呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n關西個個都死埋圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec26535958ded1f4061d06611cdf7b227e4513c","tid":610422,"uid":42180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:20:25.000Z","msg":"今次負評左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 1999"},{"pid":"c65d4bcaef37cbcbb39cd4a29b522c26436c2ff3","tid":610422,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:46:45.000Z","msg":"去長洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0981ab3502176711305d279a8234d602da742805","tid":610422,"uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aec26535958ded1f4061d06611cdf7b227e4513c","tid":610422,"uid":42180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:20:25.000Z","msg":"今次負評左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 1999"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T13:27:38.000Z","msg":"屌，是咁的<br />\n<br />\n我本身打算自己一個經廈門搭船去金門（非跟團），咁就一早買左高鐵飛，尋日預好哂時間出門口，其實都預多左d時間諗住實冇死啦，點知過關果時已經勁多join左大陸團既人，都已經心諗仆街啦會唔會趕唔切，諗住過左關就冇事啦因為我以為d旅行團都係響福田集合搭旅遊巴姐，但我完全冇諗過依家d旅行團係會搭地鐵去高鐵站搭高鐵，而且大陸搭地鐵係要過安檢，好似走難咁多人等過安檢，結果我都仲未上到地鐵已經過左高鐵班車個時間。<br />\n<br />\n尋日個人真係好頹亂打野，sorry（其實今日都好頹）"},{"pid":"6687e223eefe0b23456e7a8ed1ad9ced760656ff",